 1298                                                       ;If line inputted did not contain RUN or SCRatch com-
 1299                                                       ;mand, program continues by testing for SAVE or LOAD
 1300                                                       ;commands. If it does not find either of these com-
 1301                                                       ;mands, then operator did not input an executive com-
