 2976  139C  90           	SUB B                           ;Is positive, subtract value from 23 (decimal). If result
 2977  139D  FA A3 13     	JM OUTFLT                       ;Negative, number is too big to use fixed format.
 2978  13A0  C3 B1 13     	JMP OUTFIX                      ;Else, can use fixed format so skip next routine
 2979  13A3  AF           OUTFLT:	XRA A                           ;Clear accumulator
