 3600  18A3  F8           	RM                              ;Negative or zero
 3601  18A4  C8           	RZ                              ;In which case return to caller
 3602  18A5  C3 FC 06     	JMP TAB1                        ;Else, proceed to perform the TAB operation.
 3603                     
